# Orchestra Sync Skill

Codebase: `{{ codebase_name }}`

This skill ensures Cline workflows stay aligned with Orchestra-managed context.
Always read `orchestra/pilot.md` first.

## Use this skill when
- continuing existing tasks
- updating conventions or discovered skills
- syncing instructions across agent providers

## Steps
1. Read active tasks and notes from pilot.
2. Implement focused changes.
3. Run tests/validation.
4. Record updates through Orchestra writeback blocks.
5. Re-sync managed files when registry context changes.
